# Holds the trained buy-potential Lead Score model + card, produced by
# scripts/train_lead_score.py:
#   lead_score.cbm   - CatBoost model, loaded by lead_score.py at serve time
#   model_card.json  - version, metrics, feature order, categorical features
# Committing the artifact ships it inside the ai-agent image (see Dockerfile).
# Until a model exists here, lead_score.py is a graceful no-op.
